Package org.apache.cayenne.util

Class PersistentObjectHolder<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cayenne.util.RelationshipFault<E>
      • org.apache.cayenne.util.PersistentObjectHolder<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ValueHolder<E>

    public class PersistentObjectHolder<E>
extends RelationshipFault<E>
implements ValueHolder<E>
    A ValueHolder implementation that holds a single Persistent object related to an object used to initialize PersistentObjectHolder. Value is resolved on first access.
    Since:
    1.2
    See Also:
